		   <br><nobr><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Good [4.32]</nobr>
		   <br><img src=/shared/transp.gif width=135 border=0 height=1></td><td valign=top class=mform width=100%><p>If you're really intent on getting your Freeport faction back, you can do the inert potion quest about 2000 times to get out of scowls with the Freeport Militia.<br><br><a href="http://everquest.allakhazam.com/db/quest.html?quest=141" target=_new>http://everquest.allakhazam.com/db/quest.html?quest=141</a><br><br>The part of this quest you're concerned with is the part where you get Freeport Militia faction, with no negatives, from handing the potion in to the fake Slansin.&nbsp;&nbsp;I believe you can also pull Slansin up to the quest giver on floor three of the palace, root him and camp.  You can then redo the quest a very large number of times quite rapidly with hotkeys (about 10 seconds per completion).<br><br>So, it'll take you about 6 or 7 hours of constant clicking to get Militia faction up to an acceptable level.<br><br>Of course, you can just get a friend and maul the guards in East and West Freeport to do the quest, too.  I'd say this is a much easier method. :)</p><span class=sm>----------------------------</span><br><b>Praetor</b>, 65th Lord Protector of Ascent (Retired)<br><b>Tiresias</b>, 1st Warrior of Asura (Hopefully)</td></td></tr>
